			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The Ring of Farsight is one of many choices in the Elemental Essence quest.  Because the quest offers nice choices for every class, there is a decent amount of competition for the essence drops.  If you're just after Compsure and you're killing the elemental boss mobs for the essences anyway, there's a good chance you're in Time.  It's easier to get the Compsure items that drop in Tier 3 and Tier 4 in Time.  However, if you're not time-enabled, Korucust in Chardok B drops <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=61210">Band of the Shai'Din King</a> which has the Compsure effect, although he's not a trivial fight.  Composure items are also dropping from the raid mobs in GoD.</span></td>
